'''警衛室'''是一個以[[保安|保安]]為目的建造的建築，駐紮有哨兵或警衛。一些警衛室還有[[監獄|監獄]]之用。<ref>{{cite book | last = Kornwolf | first = James | authorlink = | coauthors = | title = Architecture and town planning in colonial North America | publisher = Johns Hopkins University Press| date = 2002 | location = Baltimore| pages = 1312 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=4bHwImC-UOUC&pg=PA1312&dq=Guardhouse+as+jail | doi = | id = | isbn = 0-8018-5986-7 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nps.gov/archive/fosc/guard3.htm |title=Guardhouse Overview |accessdate=2009-05-26 |last=info drawn from: Ketcham |first=Sally |archive-date=2009-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221085009/http://www.nps.gov/archive/fosc/guard3.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 現代警衛室 ==

21世紀的警衛室用於各種機關及[[門禁社區|門禁社區]]門口，以檢查進出入人物，一些大些的機構，警衛室會負責整個地區安全。

美國陸海軍警衛室常用的一個口號是“向下一個警衛室重複所有命令”（Repeat all calls more distant from the guardhouse than my own）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nsgreatlakes.navy.mil/otcp/ocs/gen_orders.htm|title=General Orders of a Sentry|publisher=Officer Training Command Pensacola|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061209105054/http://www.nsgreatlakes.navy.mil/otcp/ocs/gen_orders.htm|archivedate=2006-12-09|access-date=2013-09-03}}</ref> 當他們休息時，編號第一位的警衛室第一個休息。<ref>{{cite book|chapter=The Corporal|title=Customs of Service for Non Commissioned Officers and Soldiers (as practised in the Army of the United States)|date=1864|author=August V. Kautz|chapterurl=http://www.usregulars.com/COS01.html|location=Philadelphia|publisher=J. B. Lippincott & Co.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070107010558/http://www.usregulars.com/COS01.html|archivedate=2007-01-07|access-date=2013-09-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Procedures for Posting and Relieving Sentries|date=2005-11-18|work=Army Wives|url=http://www.armywives.com/index.php/component/option,com_content/task,view/id,153/Itemid,209/|publisher=Miro International Pty Ltd|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070328062702/http://www.armywives.com/index.php/component/option,com_content/task,view/id,153/Itemid,209/|archivedate=2007-03-28|access-date=2013-09-03}}</ref>

